[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating graphics configuration**\n\nI need to test the call for `getAlphaCompatibleGraphicsConfiguration` when `isWindowAlphaSupported` is true and also when there is a matching configuration. However, since `X11WindowUtils` and `getVisualID` are private, I might need to instantiate something. I’m wondering if the public API for `WindowUtils` could help, perhaps for setting things based on the OS. I should also check and read from the top to clarify my direction.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0836c459380e0dac0169f2d9ef4aec819dae49a3932eb6a4c2\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8tnyNIS4Pu1vPpsjtpwzaQZUbYo9p0z_N3I4gdE2E7JXjqMyFUL7sa2dWBT8dCpGeFf9k50blWYYFH1eD-4Ys-q_e40NISFA03WHX2XsD6q8Sj0RJ5qcbG_-rpIh4XTuT12FJOCVssPibOonPv0iI9PTd4VZHnuiGYnhOPszh3lkvt6EVlUaKoJPR2NAjOmrEvfUUNNKeOAt9v1M84G9jdl2kYrTEvYyjep-IO5v3RarKQRv9xOKzfwNLFBsROWefzfjQFbYERQp5LlOKh4BiYUh-TubLBOTu1nfx3-TEj0nFTgx7NX8fJkjxAzdMsMse5NZxPRZzjt7-jeApDh9sUujF9fKVEfUKApancGE8gK9DoRH9ljkhcVFlFbTlN9lxlYJIu-lap44ViXJUCFk7sa0lP0pFZSu_JKnt5CgNbF1Wi5RMc5Vgr_CFoo5zz6x8TBU-8tkajevYFryis-6FY2aEc_wU64Sil8AsD4CmTfo0Q0o3xD7kTm8zeHrErgftPWIeZCJMppZw9sr-dp6ExmW3d0koCJYy0Trw_iFyIacdJtBPH6w32LRMNtfL-QNM3zrd_yCG1Cxyb8yPaWXwnmCWdGsfq3ixdymn23OgSSCjrs6LTp0FhsjPiMjidOOprCDjvwO-bxFWtntGVdWdDrMsdBEffJt_A-udO4Ax2aDACRChU4nRt1b3Pt2VY-eGTkuo3YGJm0vwtjkA8cBFSj41B2WZjDdQdJzBCjyt0z_H533NSoELYvOQy-cWScg0dYhgVoIVVDXlB-ebYzjdXBfrRcRE4kKvdJ7e7I0LuPmCoosNCHSIkzReTMRUn2YM6iFHHjK3OCfmI1wFW0tg-DAGyBKcgrnzozyjZ-BqvPYlxiXd3H-zCsesrdSL8F5NvL9PkIIBlviN6uv0kFjUYgy0EnzkrxvSmU8CoTj3-TdcTZ76De7SEQz0u5Z0nE4chSt7Ph0vXCXvmqK5EcEWbRB-ZQLGzT_xVPwzBd_cPjlMnhkFpbDTn7wfSyRs1bJ3hGEDeCEj4kAuH1BH5G38VEpD18Qg6DLyHVn7b80V7YpTGiw-fKsC7iOwpFKlSSYAehoT1vYydmUdwl7xWuZrfgRmgpNTGv0a1_k0vyMCrHXddxmyV-SqLzBhukBVLW-RBb-xWrYFY96_k_lEKvGnvVeCYRgGVKigg8komLxkJoHat6V72F2TrPY11Bs040fKq61t7oNS_yXHIvGp7zOfWAJYxPirY8jQVx3ENeY0nxxJK47-mWKLd-eZL_